{"tid":310895,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿卡錫迪：因雲格愛上阿仙奴","createTime":"2017-07-06T07:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T08:17:49.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb71b440dee89e8706c28faa149ad3b2b0b958c5","tid":310895,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"　阿仙奴正式簽下了拿卡錫迪，根據BBC的報導，他的轉會費最高可達5260萬鎊，也成為了阿仙奴隊史的標王。在接受阿仙奴官網採訪時，拿卡錫迪表示加盟兵工廠是夢想成真。<br />\n<br />\n　　拿卡錫迪說：「我非常高興也非常驕傲，因為阿仙奴是一家傳奇的球會。在我小時候，因為亨利和很多法國球員的關係，我總是夢想著能夠為阿仙奴效力，今天夢想實現了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　這名法國前鋒還透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">雲格是說服他加盟球隊的另一個重要原因</span>，拿卡錫迪說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我喜歡有歷史的球會。雲格在這裡執教了很長時間，這也證明這是一家穩定的球會，我也很喜歡這一點。隊里還有很多法國球員，這會讓我適應這裡變得更容易一些。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n　　「在我看來，阿仙奴是英格蘭踢得最好看的球隊，所以我真的非常想要來到這裡。」<br />\n<br />\n爺爺又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7688144823966a102d633e3ffd1f2a40c83ca00","tid":310895,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:28:58.000Z","msg":"啵"},{"pid":"9f7b2249a9cffe9659cc084a062ae1131d26a3a4","tid":310895,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"夠穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3d6452901b5d1dbc6d6c0c95ef5bc091040fa0","tid":310895,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺千秋萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae16ceea5da1dc7ff7abc4aa8990d2dd6fb3f3f","tid":310895,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9b4ffd5e39b334fa24df3a233fcca4d53ffcbe","tid":310895,"uid":36566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces